    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="How should I handle revision requests?" class="article-title">
          How should I handle revision requests?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>We do not recommend accepting revision requests with the Requests feature.</p>
<p>Fans are invited to send in a new request after the request is complete if they wish for revisions.</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

